name: AiseLife Limited Edition Poster #1
description:
Limited Edition Poster

25 Prints - signed, numbered & dated

I wanted to create something that directly expressed my liking for Marijuana and the things about me that people seem surprised about when they notice such as the fact that I do smoke herb and have a tattoo on my wrist.   The "s" represent a time period in my art where I was obsessed with squid tentacles.   

You will receive this piece shrink wrapped and in a UPS Tube Package.
